explanation: [0-0] A young man in a red sweatshirt lies on his stomach with his hands on either side of his body, staring at a purple viscous object in front of him. The background is an open ground with trees and blue sky and white clouds in the distance.

Immediately, the high heel slowly steps on the purple viscous object. Subsequently, the high heel steps on the purple viscous object and begins to squeeze it downwards with force. The purple viscous object is then squeezed and deformed by the high heel, expanding outwards from the heel.
